title: AHS Apocalypse Episode 5 Review SPOILERS!!
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I don’t think cordillia’s powers are weakening because there is a new supreme I think they are weakening because there are forces more powerful than her in general. My theory is that Mallory is not a witch. Micheal has authority over witches and worlocks enough to defeat them. With Mallory he was SHOOK. I think Mallory is an angel.
Ryan Murphy and Brad Falchuck and the whole cast and crew killed it this season and it's only episode 5 !!
I couldn't control my emotions and not cry when Stevie started singing and Misty danced. I was just singing and crying
It's not fair for Cordelia to fade away so soon. She's only been supreme for like 7 years, the last few Supremes were well over middle age before their successors flowered. This is not fair.
